
	Deployment Descriptor	-	web.xml
	
	In old application:
		We requested for a resources which was a web page.
		
	But in modern application we may request for a class methods or
	an independent function.
	
	In servlet, we write HTML in Java programs.
	In JSP, we write Java in HTML.
	
	
	Model			-	PHP class/function	-	Data Access
	View			-	PHP in HTML
	Controller		-	PHP class/function	-	Request Handling
	
	
	Model			-	Servlet
	View			-	JSP
	Controller		-	Servlet
	
